p.font: A depiction of what a distributed computing environment may look like. Tasks could be concurrently executed through several cloud computing services which access large files stored in the shared file server. Another task may submitted as a batch job to a high performance computing cluster that also needs access to the shared file server. Links between these resources represent a logical network topology, however the underlying physical network topology can differ.
